:{{DIcon|Talk}} How's the kitchen holding up?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_835163303-->
::'''Phainon:''' Things are going smoothly. The farmland's supplying plenty of ingredients, and our signature dishes are a big hit with the customers. We're just a bit short on hands... the kitchen's absolute chaos every day.
